"Automated manufacturing order bill of materials define how semi-finished "
"bottles are packaged into boxes and how boxes can be split into beer bottles."
msgstr ""
"Automatiserede produktionsordres styklister beskriver, hvordan halvfabrikata "
"som flasker pakkes i kasser, og hvordan kasserne kan opdeles i enkeltstående "
"ølflasker."

