msgstr ""
"I produktionsappen kan du oprette en stykliste for at definere, hvordan "
"øllet skal fremstilles."

#. module: micro_brewery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:micro_brewery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"It could also be interesting for your customer to buy souvenirs, gifts or "
"simply some pack of beers after the visit. You can have both a bar/"
"restaurant and a shop or you can manage both from the same"
msgstr ""
"Det kunne også være interessant for dine kunder at købe souvenirs, gaver "
"eller blot en kasse øl efter besøget. Du kan have både en bar/restaurant og "
"en butik – eller drive begge dele under samme tag"

